Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.21,0:04:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}直到我们全都无法动弹为止
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.76,0:04:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}然后他们就能不战而胜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.64,0:04:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}轻松夺走奄奄一息的艾伦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.73,0:04:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}现在 敌方大型巨人都排成一排没有行动
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.27,0:04:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}可以确定它们是在充当围栏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.49,0:04:24.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}团 团长
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.95,0:04:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}铠甲巨人马上就要爬上来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.57,0:04:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}而且 还不清楚鲁特尔德在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.54,0:04:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.71,0:04:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}现在最要担心的问题是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.54,0:04:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}我们会眼睁睁看着马匹被莱纳和贝鲁特尔德杀死
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.05,0:04:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}那样一来…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.34,0:04:45.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}你终于打算下命令了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.97,0:04:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}早知道就该先把早饭吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.18,0:04:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}迪鲁克分队和马雷涅分队
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.39,0:04:54.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}你们和内门的克拉斯分队一起死守马匹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.94,0:04:59.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}利威尔分队和汉吉分队去干掉铠甲巨人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.23,0:05:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}各分队听从指挥 使用雷枪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.28,0:05:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}无论如何都要完成任务
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.36,0:05:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}此时此刻 这场战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.12,0:05:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}关乎人类的生死存亡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.37,0:05:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}让我们再一次为人类
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.71,0:05:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}献上心脏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.42,0:05:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.04,0:05:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}听到没有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.34,0:05:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}把过来杀马的巨人全部干掉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.22,0:05:24.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.17,0:05:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}等一下 利威尔 阿尔敏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.14,0:05:29.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}虽然我叫利威尔分队去那边了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.55,0:05:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}不过你一个人留在这边 利威尔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.31,0:05:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}你要我无视艾伦去保护马匹吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.89,0:05:35.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.15,0:05:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}然后趁机干掉那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.98,0:05:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}干掉野兽巨人的任务
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.73,0:05:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}非你莫属
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.15,0:05:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.86,0:05:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}我刚才连一个铠甲小鬼都没能杀死
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.16,0:05:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}就拿那家伙的首级来弥补刚才的失态吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.25,0:05:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}阿尔敏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.21,0:06:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}我有一个对付铠甲巨人的计划
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.52,0:06:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.79,0:06:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}决定人类命运的战局之一
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.80,0:06:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}与铠甲巨人的战斗 就交给汉吉和你指挥了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.61,0:06:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.07,0:06:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}都集中在一个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.53,0:06:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}杀死那些马 然后离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.45,0:06:35.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}仅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.45,0:06:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}不论利威尔兵长有多强
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.37,0:06:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}都终归不是我们战士长的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.26,0:06:48.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}好险
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.43,0:06:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}那时要是再晚一瞬把意识转移至全身
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.30,0:06:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}真的就当场死亡了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.39,0:06:59.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}不过为什么会想到要调查墙壁内部啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.65,0:07:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}阿尔敏 是你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.94,0:07:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}算了 无所谓了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.32,0:07:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}这样一来 我们那漫长的旅程终于可以结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.00,0:07:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}埃尔文·史密斯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.79,0:07:25.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}不要犹豫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.17,0:07:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}要优先杀死马匹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.72,0:07:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}什…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.40,0:07:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}艾伦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.73,0:07:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}为什么你主动现身了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.02,0:07:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}我们就是冲着你来的啊 你应该很清楚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.44,0:07:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}你到底想做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.70,0:07:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}难道他想从南边翻墙逃跑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.12,0:08:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}他一个人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.25,0:08:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}就算没有马匹 也能用巨人之力逃到托洛斯特区
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.75,0:08:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}要是他跑了 我们就没有理由留在这里战斗了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.67,0:08:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}就算在这里歼灭了调查兵团
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.93,0:08:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}他只用两个月就学会了硬质化
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.05,0:08:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}让他逃回墙内就太危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.06,0:08:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}要是让他完全掌握坐标之力就晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.31,0:08:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}不对 等等 奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.11,0:08:28.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}如果他真的想逃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.07,0:08:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}应该先用立体机动移动到东边或西边的墙壁上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.55,0:08:32.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}然后再巨人化才对
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.11,0:08:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}为什么要特地在被墙壁包围的希干希纳区里面巨人化
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.45,0:08:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.46,0:08:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}他们的目的 是让我把目标从马匹转向艾伦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.55,0:08:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}都不给我思考的时间是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.22,0:09:01.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}团长真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.27,0:09:04.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}亏我好不容易爬了上来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.53,0:09:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}好 上钩了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.70,0:09:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}让艾伦当诱饵？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.61,0:09:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}是的 这是埃尔文团长的指示
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.24,0:09:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}没想到会让艾伦充当诱饵去保护马匹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.08,0:09:24.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}怎么这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.42,0:09:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}要是莱纳选择了先杀马匹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.96,0:09:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}不对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.04,0:09:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}他应该会去追艾伦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.21,0:09:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}如果莱纳选择去杀马匹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.63,0:09:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}就会放任艾伦绕到背后袭击野兽巨人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.01,0:09:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}然后野兽巨人就会被利威尔等人和艾伦夹击
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.18,0:09:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}埃尔文的指示是到这一步吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.76,0:09:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}是 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.27,0:09:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}就算不这么顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.36,0:09:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}只要艾伦有逃跑的动作
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.48,0:09:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}敌人的行动也会被搅乱 包围网就会瓦解
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.49,0:09:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}只是不知道莱纳能不能想到这个份上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.37,0:10:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}如果是他的话 应该是能想到的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.46,0:10:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.46,0:10:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}在希干希纳区内迎击铠甲巨人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.46,0:10:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}请等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.84,0:10:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}还有一个问题需要注意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.05,0:10:19.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}贝鲁特尔德还潜伏在某处
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.85,0:10:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}上次艾伦差一点就要打败莱纳了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.18,0:10:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}结果遭到贝鲁特尔德那强大的突然袭击
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.52,0:10:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}被他们给掳走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.98,0:10:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}我有一个简单的对策
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.36,0:10:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}在远离墙壁的地方战斗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.16,0:10:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}我战胜过你一次
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.46,0:10:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}虽然那可能只是运气好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.46,0:10:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}差一点就赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.26,0:10:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}一对一的话 我能赢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.09,0:11:03.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}论单纯的格斗能力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.85,0:11:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}亚妮要比你难对付多了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.13,0:11:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}你知道这里是什么地方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.05,0:11:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}这个地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.31,0:11:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}是我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.90,0:11:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}是我们的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.02,0:11:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}故乡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.28,0:12:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}我一定要夺回来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.65,0:12:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}要把你们赶尽杀绝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.49,0:12:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}夺回被你们夺走的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.95,0:12:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\bord3\shad3\fsp0\an1\1c&H0080FF&\b1}{\u1}现在可以公开的情报\N\N雷枪\N{\r\fs16\bord3\shad3\fsp0\an1\1c&H0080FF&\b1}\N\N为了对抗坚硬的铠甲巨人，\N使用中央宪兵秘密持有的技术开发出的武器。\N虽然使用难度较大，但能将冲击集中在一点，\N发挥出落雷般的威力。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.95,0:12:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.76,0:12:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}新兵 把剩下的马匹都转移到西边去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.84,0:12:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}迪鲁克分队去掩护新兵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.68,0:12:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}去哪里 马尔洛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.47,0:12:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}要把马牵到哪里去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.89,0:12:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}命 命令说不要让马集中在一个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.35,0:12:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}这里不行 要更远
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.90,0:12:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}3-4米级从东边来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.24,0:12:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}那就是 巨人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.21,0:12:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}利威尔兵长
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.57,0:12:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}趁现在 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.42,0:12:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}快点把小家伙都收拾掉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.67,0:13:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}在野兽巨人行动之前
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.63,0:13:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}不允许出现伤亡 一个人都不准死
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.18,0:13:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.72,0:13:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}可恶 我受够了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.77,0:13:13.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}弱者很快就会死掉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.35,0:13:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}没用的家伙都滚一边去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.36,0:13:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}和3-4米级陷入苦战
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.28,0:13:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}好几个地方都出现了伤员
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.20,0:13:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}如今的调查兵团 已经不像过去那样强大了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.62,0:13:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}但是 如果不付出这种代价
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.29,0:13:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}我们是绝对走不到现在的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.92,0:13:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}训练兵时代 我经常和同伴聊起自己和父亲的假说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.30,0:13:51.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}还说要进入调查兵团去证明这个假说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.35,0:13:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}但是 不知为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.93,0:13:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}自从进入调查兵团 我便再也没有和人说起这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.23,0:14:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}不 不对
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.53,0:14:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}我知道为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.32,0:14:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}因为我发现了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.70,0:14:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}只有我一个人是在为自己而战
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.29,0:14:16.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}只有我一个人沉浸在自己的梦中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.00,0:14:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}不知何时开始 我有了部下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.59,0:14:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}并且这样鼓舞同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.26,0:14:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}「为人类献上心脏吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.47,0:14:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}我就这样欺骗着同伴 欺骗着自己
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.48,0:14:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}在堆积如山的尸骸上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.86,0:14:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}孤独站立着
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.24,0:14:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}即便如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.37,0:14:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}我仍然满脑子都是那间地下室
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.20,0:14:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}就算这次作战失败
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.54,0:15:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}说不定也能在死前进入那间地下室
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.50,0:15:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}进入格里沙·耶格尔留下的地下室
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.84,0:15:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}一窥世界的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.73,0:15:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}不枉我辛苦实验
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.15,0:15:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}这拳头很有效
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.86,0:15:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}把硬质化集中在一点 会变得更加坚固
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.78,0:15:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}他这种覆盖全身的铠甲就像薄冰一样 一敲即碎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.96,0:15:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}你太慢了 蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.18,0:15:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.06,0:16:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}汉吉分队长
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.22,0:16:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}还不行 必须一次成功
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.77,0:16:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}耐心等着 要相信艾伦会为我们制造最佳机会
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.82,0:16:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}这个铁棒就是新武器吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.57,0:16:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}至少也叫它枪嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.91,0:17:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}技术组没有辜负我的期待
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.54,0:17:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}引入了中央宪兵秘密持有的新技术
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.71,0:17:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}我提出的要求是制造一个能对抗铠甲巨人的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.30,0:17:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}对抗铠甲巨人？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.76,0:17:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}在铠甲巨人面前 我们的刀根本一无是处
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.22,0:17:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}只要敌人的硬质化不露出破绽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.43,0:17:27.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}我们就只能在一旁看着艾伦和铠甲巨人战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.65,0:17:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}确实
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.73,0:17:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}当时铠甲巨人带着艾伦扬长而去 我们根本拦不住
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.07,0:17:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}那个时候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.70,0:17:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}要是团长没有将大群巨人吸引过来…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.66,0:17:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}现阶段 对抗铠甲巨人的主要方法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.00,0:17:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}是巨人化的艾伦使用的绞技和关节技
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.25,0:17:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}前几天的实验中获得的硬质化拳头也值得期待
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.26,0:17:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}但是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.34,0:18:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}仅凭这些武器 想让作战获得成功是很困难的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.10,0:18:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}虽然堵住墙壁的洞也很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.52,0:18:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}但最重要的是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.23,0:18:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}我们必须杀死墙壁的破坏者 也就是莱纳和贝鲁特尔德
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.44,0:18:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}要用这个枪去刺铠甲巨人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.24,0:18:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}演示一下更快
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.66,0:18:20.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}到外面去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.42,0:18:32.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}威力正如你们所见
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.42,0:18:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}就像被雷劈了一样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.76,0:18:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}所以它的名字叫「雷枪」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.26,0:18:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}不过 这个是否真的能击败铠甲巨人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.80,0:18:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}不实战一次也不好说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.60,0:18:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}它对普通巨人有效
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.98,0:18:50.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}但要想让它击中铠甲巨人 得下点功夫才行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.75,0:19:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.35,0:19:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}果然只凭我一个人还是打不过艾伦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.56,0:19:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}只能用这个了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.57,0:19:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}就是现在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.49,0:19:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}士兵行动了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.33,0:19:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}我知道他们从刚才开始就把我包围了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.75,0:19:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}但是 士兵的刀刃根本没用
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.79,0:19:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}我可是全身都覆盖着铠甲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.92,0:19:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}那种东西根本不能伤我分毫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.02,0:20:07.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}什…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.57,0:20:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.07,0:20:24.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}不 还不够
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.24,0:20:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}雷枪破坏力极强 甚至可能威胁到使用者
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.33,0:20:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}如果像平时用刀刃斩击一样 将枪头射入巨人体内的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.58,0:20:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}那么在身体飞向巨人的时候 就会被波及到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.59,0:20:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}因此 要使用雷枪进行攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.30,0:20:44.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}只能在目标周围有足够多立体物的情况下
